title: A Knight Templar abroad; or, Reminiscences of travel beyond the sea
author: Cord, W. Harlan.
snippet: We will begin our quotations from the pamphlet above referred to, by giving a summary of a paper read at the reception alluded to, as having occurred on September 5th, 1881, on " The Records etc., in the Archives of the York Lodge," by Bro. J. Todd, P. M., York Lodge.
